—ЩRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-04-10-twin0085.mdЩ@3c35b4c295f1d0098d567d7a19f76d8735eea5846844074f0739da04fbcf0095іThis Week in Nu #85‘§NushellЪ	,ilius added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3249] autocompletions for aliases and custom commands
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3257] TiB and PiB filesizes
andrasio added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3252] ``any?``
 and 
``all?``
 commands
, removed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3258] help shell
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3261] better support for startup commands to the scope
, started to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3283] simplify runnable contexts
, moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3287] config loading to load from memory
, removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3294] arg serialiation from 
``str``
 subcommands
mhmdanas removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3262] the broken 
``yr``
 and 
``mon``
 duration units
LhKipp refactored 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3265] the config commands
fdncred bumped 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3267] sysinfo
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3291] the default prompt
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3293] ansi rgb fb
jonathandturner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3270] switched commands to sync iterator style
, fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3280] busy-wait for externals
, began 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3281] migrating away from arg serialization
, prevented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3285] loading of config in autoview when not needed
, simplified the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3288] default features list
, moved from 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3289] representing codeblocks to Arc of Block instead of Block
, simplified 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3292] how 
``length``
 calculated the length of a table
DonnotPanic fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3271] a crash with out-of-range timestamps
ammkrn prevented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3278] using trash-based 
``rm``
 if the feature wasn't enabled
schrieveslaach prevented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3286] whitespace entries from being added to history
